<div class="language-markdown codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-markdown codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token title important punctuation" style="color:#393A34">#</span><span class="token title important"> ğŸ’£ Comprendre les Failles SQLi : Le Guide Complet pour DÃ©butants</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">La sÃ©curitÃ© web est un pilier essentiel du dÃ©veloppement moderne. Pourtant, une vulnÃ©rabilitÃ© vieille comme le web continue de faire des ravages : </span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">lâ€™injection SQL (SQLi)</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain">. </span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">Dans cet article, je vous propose une plongÃ©e claire et structurÃ©e dans le monde des failles SQLi : de la dÃ©couverte de colonnes avec </span><span class="token code-snippet code keyword" style="color:#00009f">`UNION`</span><span class="token plain">, aux techniques de contournement de WAF, en passant par l'exfiltration de donnÃ©es. Un vÃ©ritable couteau suisse pour mieux comprendre cette menace â€” et apprendre Ã  sâ€™en protÃ©ger.</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token hr punctuation" style="color:#393A34">---</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token title important punctuation" style="color:#393A34">##</span><span class="token title important"> ğŸ§  Câ€™est quoi une injection SQL ?</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">Lâ€™injection SQL consiste Ã  insÃ©rer du code SQL malveillant dans une requÃªte prÃ©vue pour interagir avec une base de donnÃ©es. Elle survient gÃ©nÃ©ralement via des champs non filtrÃ©s comme un formulaire de connexion ou une URL.</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token bold content">Exemple simple :</span><span class="token bold punctuation" style="color:#393A34">**</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">```sql</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">Input : ' OR 1=1 --</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">RequÃªte : SELECT * FROM users WHERE username = '' OR 1=1 --' AND password = ''</span><br></span></code></pre><div class="buttonGroup__atx"><button type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard" title="Copy" class="clean-btn"><span class="copyButtonIcons_eSgA"